archimate:BusinessFunction.name: Implementation
archimate:BusinessFunction.documentation:
As stated in ISO/IEC/IEEE 15288, [6.4.7.1] The purpose of the Implementation process is to realize a specified system element.
See detailed description in the INCOSE Handbook v.4, page 77
